Class MulticastSubject<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • spritz.MulticastSubject<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventEmitter<T>, Publisher<T>, Subject<T>

    public final class MulticastSubject<T>
extends Object
implements Subject<T>
    A PublishOperator that emits items to currently subscribed Subscriber instances and terminal events to current or late Subscriber instances.
